{"tid":2253041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人類首次在銀河系之外發現一顆行星","createTime":"2020-10-22T01:49:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T01:56:59.000Z","uid":138707,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a40fe42a15a6574ea9d079ced087917ba160cba4","tid":2253041,"uid":138707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T01:49:39.000Z","msg":"在這之前，科學家發現的「系外行星」，都是位於銀河系內、太陽系以外的行星，全名是「太陽系外行星」。哈佛-史密森尼天文中心的科學家在近期發表在一份研究中稱，發現了第一顆位於銀河系以外的「河外」行星。<br />\n<br />\n發現太陽系之外的行星難度已經很高，科學家在1992年才發現第一顆。<br />\n<br />\n太陽同銀河系外行星差好遠wow，寫新聞條友真係唔識架禍。"},{"pid":"d9d86891132380892de8ca861554cee982594900","tid":2253041,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T01:56:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2009.08987\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fabs%2F2009.08987&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPcsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=c357bd69\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2009.08987</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}